CHANGELOG
=========

1.3.0
---
* Enhanced a11y by using ARIA roles.
* Choose folder before colearning a shared deck.
* Added a new navigation item of all shared decks.


1.2.0
---

* Change icon and wording of the former "Mitlernen" to "Abonnieren" of shared decks.
* Fix error when requesting the subscription of a shared deck.


1.1.0
---

* Add PDF export of decks.
* Fix creating and updating cards by purifying HTML.
* Fix display of decks and their learning statistics on small devices.
* Fix translation errors.
